query:
SELECT v.*, f.nome as formando_nome, f.turmaId 
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id 
WHERE DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(v.createdAt / 1000)) = '2026-06-14' 
ORDER BY v.createdAt
